sequenceDiagram
  participant App as App / mongosh
  participant Mongos as mongos
  participant Shards as Shards tic/tac/toe
  participant Connect as Kafka Connect
  participant Kafka as Kafka broker
  participant Sink as Mongo sink + SMT

  App->>Mongos: insert/update demo.demo_items
  Mongos->>Shards: routed document writes
  Note over Shards: Change streams on shard primaries
  Connect->>Mongos: MongoDbConnector polls change stream
  Connect->>Kafka: produce demomongo.demo.demo_items
  Kafka->>Sink: consume records
  Note over Sink: ExtractNewDocumentState flattens Debezium envelope for BSON
  Sink->>Mongos: write demo.demo_items_from_kafka
  Note over App,Mongos: demo_items_from_kafka not in collection.include.list → no CDC loop
